apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, this dynamic emoji captures a powerful moment of strength with its depiction of a man with a rich, dark skin tone lifting weights.  The characteristic Apple design imbues the figure with a sense of muscular definition through smooth gradients and realistic lighting, highlighting the exertion of the lift.  Its rounded, approachable form and subtle sheen convey a feeling of achievement, fitness, and personal accomplishment, making it a vibrant addition to any message about goals or physical activity on Apple devices.
